occupations.title: Management Consultant
occupations.description: Assists organizations to achieve greater efficiency and solve organizational problems.

occupations.title: Marketing Specialist

occupations.title: Early Childhood Teacher

occupations.title: University Lecturer

occupations.title: Bricklayer

occupations.title: Electrician (General)
occupations.description: Installs, maintains, repairs and tests electrical equipment, wiring and control systems.

occupations.title: Enrolled Nurse

occupations.title: Community Worker

occupations.title: Chef

occupations.title: Waiter
